. Possible biological implications of the results\nare discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Mar 2014 22:24:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Dec 2014 16:46:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2015 19:32:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-29"}
