 from biological optima.\nPersistent correlation between states in DNA sequence across spatial\nseparations of any length--a characteristic signature of quantum\nentanglement--may be explained by such a physical mechanism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Mar 2014 01:45:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-24"}
